# Copy to `.env.local` in this directory (gitignored). Do not commit real credentials.
#
# AWS credentials: set once in infra/envs/dev/.env.aws (see infra/envs/dev/.env.aws.example).
# This file is for service-specific secrets only (IAM bootstrap, Bedrock bearer token, …).

# IAM deployment admin — canonical source for local + AWS deploy (``make scaffold-secrets``).
# Also used by empty-logins bootstrap (IAM_AUTO_BOOTSTRAP_ADMIN_ON_EMPTY, default true on AWS).
# IAM_BOOTSTRAP_FIRST_NAME=
# IAM_BOOTSTRAP_LAST_NAME=
# IAM_BOOTSTRAP_EMAIL=
# IAM_BOOTSTRAP_PASSWORD=
#
# ``make reset-iam`` recreates users+logins from RESET_IAM_* (can match bootstrap above):
# RESET_IAM_FIRST_NAME=
# RESET_IAM_LAST_NAME=
# RESET_IAM_USERNAME=
# RESET_IAM_PASSWORD=
